longBusinessSummary: OncoZenge AB (publ), a pharmaceutical company, engages in the development of treatment for pain relief in patients suffering from oral pain caused by radiation therapy and chemotherapy for cancer in Sweden. It offers BupiZenge, which has completed Phase 2 clinical trial for the treatment of pain in the oral cavity. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is headquartered in Bromma, Sweden.
